## II.4 Deployment

**Serving Mode:** Batch Deployment  
**Notebook:** `06_batch_deployment.ipynb`

### Deployment Configuration
- Model loaded from Azure Data Lake curated zone
- Input: 12 features (rank_diff, pts_diff, odds_diff, etc.)
- Output: prediction (0=Player2 wins, 1=Player1 wins)
- Batch scored 67,433 records
- Results saved to: `abfss://curated@tennisdatalake60105845.dfs.core.windows.net/predictions/batch_v1/`

### Input/Output Interface
| Input Feature | Type | Description |
|---------------|------|-------------|
| rank_diff | Integer | Rank_1 - Rank_2 |
| pts_diff | Integer | Points_1 - Points_2 |
| odds_diff | Double | Odd_1 - Odd_2 |
| p1_higher_ranked | Binary | 1 if Rank_1 < Rank_2 |
| is_grand_slam | Binary | 1 if Grand Slam |
| is_hard_court | Binary | 1 if Hard surface |
| is_clay_court | Binary | 1 if Clay surface |
| is_best_of_5 | Binary | 1 if Best of 5 sets |
| Rank_1 | Integer | Player 1 ATP rank |
| Rank_2 | Integer | Player 2 ATP rank |
| year | Integer | Match year |
| month | Integer | Match month |

| Output | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| prediction | Double | 0.0=P2 wins, 1.0=P1 wins |

---

## II.5 Deployment Validation

### Sanity Checks
| Test Case | Expected | Actual | Result |
|-----------|----------|--------|--------|
| Rank 1 vs Rank 100 (Grand Slam) | P1 wins | P1 wins | ✅ |
| Rank 200 vs Rank 5 | P2 wins | P2 wins | ✅ |
| Equal players (Rank 50 vs 52) | Either | P2 wins | ✅ |

### Full Dataset Results
- **Total predictions:** 67,433
- **Correct predictions:** 46,943
- **Full dataset accuracy:** 69.61%
- **Consistency:** Offline and batch predictions match ✅

